{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f5e6f67a0e","title":"右派言论——“反右派是变相的肃反”","origin":"《“鸣”、“放”选集（四）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编印，1957年11月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5c05fc0a43","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"f5e6f67a0e"}],"tags":[{"id":"625c516d2c","name":"朝鲜战争","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0c430b6e51","name":"山西医学院"},{"id":"45710ec53a","name":"王启一"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"32dace2ef5","type":"title","text":"右派言论——“反右派是变相的肃反”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f5e6f67a0e"},{"id":"075cc04e13","type":"authors","text":"山西医学院王启一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f5e6f67a0e"},{"id":"856a4af10c","type":"subtitle","text":"（王启一：山西医学院学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f5e6f67a0e"},{"id":"d99071df65","type":"paragraph","text":"“土改对自己无教育”。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f5e6f67a0e"},{"id":"151648b16c","type":"paragraph","text":"“三反、五反运动是共产党太厉害，逼死人”。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f5e6f67a0e"},{"id":"fc12436007","type":"paragraph","text":"“镇反运动是每一个执政党总是要对相反的阶级来一下镇反。与蒋介石大屠杀一样，你杀我，我杀你”。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f5e6f67a0e"},{"id":"450f66863f","type":"paragraph","text":"“朝鲜战争是一个碗不响，二个碗叮当，是两个社会制度的斗争”。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f5e6f67a0e"},{"id":"7f42f07749","type":"paragraph","text":"“我院肃反搞糟了，肃反被刘院长搞糟了。刘院长说肃反成绩是主要的，缺点是难免的是公式化”。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f5e6f67a0e"},{"id":"f749ff6caa","type":"paragraph","text":"“一系列的社会运动改革，不能好好念书。这次反右派斗争又不准请假，没有一点民主，简直要窒息”。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f5e6f67a0e"},{"id":"aec563bd74","type":"paragraph","text":"“在各个运动中‘提高’了，为了不让别人抓住，少开口为妙。鸣放是摆啹头（骗人）以后总要整的，还是不鸣不放好。章、罗、储、葛的言论有力、有理、有风趣。储安平是构词不当，举的例子还是很有说服力的；12个副总理没有一个是党外人士，这一点共产党也无理解释。反右派斗争是算旧账、揭老底、一棍子打死人。是变相的肃反。共产党手法高明，先说整党内，现在反过来整党外。”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f5e6f67a0e"}],"page":{"id":"668f0a849e","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f5e6f67a0e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}